edBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:52:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T08:41:54.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站    <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2FyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=b6f9b5b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"f4f72d4036cfc25f195fd73a069442af1bc11d2d","tid":1776593,"uid":335891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08a5552a608474a6637dbcddac37b84562156181","tid":1776593,"uid":5843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33a557747f9e076cf54410305fa5ea0d7a1d34a1","tid":1776593,"uid":173307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:55:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:58:14.000Z","msg":"抑鬱係咁上下，呢排打仗已經開少咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T12:48:54.000Z","msg":"絲打 有咩事喺到講 乖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}